  "logNo": "221161550744",
  "title": "원장님들의 교육&강의타임 [이수한의원 남성역한의원 사당동한의원]",
  "addDate": "2017. 12. 12.",
  "categoryNo": "43",
  "parentCategoryNo": "1",
  "url": "https://blog.naver.com/PostView.naver?blogId=isuhani&logNo=221161550744",
  "html_size": 192886,
  "body": "<div id=\"post-view221161550744\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea221161550744\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'957317_10';\" class=\"view\"><p>이수한의원의 내부공사 관계로 진료를 못하고 있죠...</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>공사기간이 3주라서 대부분 환자분들께서</p><p>\"좋으시겠어요 3주동안 쉬어서..\" \"쉬니까 좋겠어~\" \"아이고 휴가네~\" \"3주동안 놀겠네~\" 라고&nbsp;</p><p>많이들 말씀하시더라구요 ㅋㅋ</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>하지만 우리 이수한의원 식구들은 쉬지 않고</p><p>원장님께서 우리직원들과 앞으로 더 새로워질 이수한의원을 위해</p><p>매일매일 교육을 해주셨습니다</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>기본적인거부터 시작해서 환자분들을 위한 것들을 알려주셨고요</p><p><br /></p><p>아래사진 보시면&nbsp;</p><p>대부분 환자분들은 허리와 골반이 많이 아프셔서</p><p>척추뼈도 그리시고 허리 디스크 부위 등 골반뼈도 그려서 설명해주시고 계신 장면입니다</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/522532a1e4595ed7.jpg\" width=\"480\" height=\"270\" style=\"cursor: pointer; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); rwidth:480px; rheight:270px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTJfMTkz/MDAxNTEzMDc4MDAxNTc1.YyBgXousCdwdIzrdNFyN9K59Y7fuwZUob27qvYEtzHog.PTkRB9K97tO8z2oZVG_UClZOfAdvlI2cAtdxm9-oviMg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181912786.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E417398')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/522532a1e4595ed7.jpg\"><br style=\"clear:both;\" /><br style=\"clear:both;\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/a9558593a9a40500.jpg\" width=\"480\" height=\"270\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth:480px; rheight:270px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTJfMTIx/MDAxNTEzMDc4MDAxNzUz.Gl82I-M04FCGGF4Bsv-1Nwa1Gw-2AAm9ZO012QI7hAwg.UK1OkWRbZctkxoWViYYMw_kQV0Sw5fT3-QDq-DqnY_Ag.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181913026.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E417398')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/a9558593a9a40500.jpg\"></p><p><br /></p><p>오른쪽에 티비를 보시면</p><p>근육 인대 등 파워포인트로 파일도 만들어오셔서&nbsp;</p><p>하나부터 다 설명해주시고요</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>개인적으로 원장님께서 교육 해주시면</p><p>귀에 쏙쏙 들어와서 너무 재밌습니다</p><p><br /></p><p>우리 직원들이 열심히 잘 듣고 배워서</p><p>치료실에서 환자분들 치료해드릴때 꼭 잘 활용하겠습니다</p><div><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><br /></div><div>12월1일 금요일은 원장님께서 경의대학교에 강의가&nbsp;있던날입니다</div><div>우리 직원들 아침부터 경희대에 가서 원장님 강의를 들었어요</div><p><br style=\"clear:both;\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/ba2b65afb8cc61a3.jpg\" width=\"480\" height=\"640\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth:480px; rheight:640px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTJfODEg/MDAxNTEzMDc4MDAxOTA2.2kyc4DFO6vYbx2YbSA1NrdyLS7f5QXx0u9N3-1J0bd4g.IzItGlvErSv4WdLTMt9CfsQhTLuv7N-cE_Oh25lPH1sg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181838895.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E417398')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/ba2b65afb8cc61a3.jpg\"></p><p><br /></p><p>경희대에 가면 사자 큰거 한마리가 이렇게 자리잡고 서있어요. 좀 멋있죠 사자? ㅋㅋ</p><p><br style=\"clear:both;\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/2df202ff07a3693f.jpg\" width=\"480\" height=\"360\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth:480px; rheight:360px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTJfMjcy/MDAxNTEzMDc4MDAyMDM1.bl_f6ekAYF4TS_eBuoH6SiGHkkdLDAvZvGo18sbSm3og.Nh1GZlgtOdbWO5_Sdf5hJLRtfrGP2Tk7G7w_clenswEg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181837838.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E417398')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/2df202ff07a3693f.jpg\"><br style=\"clear:both;\" /><br style=\"clear:both;\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/6155ea2db786706d.jpg\" width=\"480\" height=\"360\" style=\"cursor: pointer; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); rwidth:480px; rheight:360px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTJfMTEx/MDAxNTEzMDc4MDAyMTY3.gpeM49_-UZ-QtKyv4gnIFq-Z4p3Ae-UvWi8wwlD2-d8g.71EpHCtKAyctIUwKvSLt44inCA8F-MKPIebpMng3SVIg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181838093.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E417398')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/6155ea2db786706d.jpg\"><br style=\"clear:both;\" /><br style=\"clear:both;\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/1fd46ea7380a4e25.jpg\" width=\"480\" height=\"360\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth:480px; rheight:360px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTJfMTE5/MDAxNTEzMDc4MDAyMzMz.DsCOymwzIPjXBickk6g3pI2k1uEmZLGfgnFsROOjWjIg.n_LQ0XlfkYYEwYKpzmt-9YZrS70J-XcYBjmFV0iv9lEg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181838332.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E417398')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/1fd46ea7380a4e25.jpg\"><br style=\"clear:both;\" /><br style=\"clear:both;\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/dbf229caf4cc81da.jpg\" width=\"480\" height=\"360\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth:480px; rheight:360px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTJfMjEw/MDAxNTEzMDc4MDAyNTY5.8hvIc1Ppu99Bz9foqXBiZ7IRSZc1WDPwT10ZLFHJJlQg.GuVm2-JMkgxWhMTL4tpa738mx0PDTJy9waahD8H3xuAg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181838605.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E417398')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/dbf229caf4cc81da.jpg\">&nbsp;</p><p>이날 역시 우리원장님은 설명해주시느라 바쁘셨습니다</p><p><br /></p><p>강의하실때도 귀에 쏙쏙~</p><p><br /></p><p>너무 많은 대학생들과 같이 강의를 들으니</p><p>마치 저도&nbsp;대학생인 기분이었어요 ㅋㅋ</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>어제는&nbsp;나원장님께서 담당이신 성장의 대해 교육해주셨는데</p><p>사진찍는걸 깜빡했네요 ㅡㅡ;;</p><p><br /></p><p>나원장님도 교육해주실때 너무 재밌게 해주시는데..</p><p>공책에 적으면서 듣고 질문도 많아서&nbsp;사진찍을 생각을 못했네요 ㅠㅠ</p><p>아쉽다...</p><p><br /></p><p>(내일 나원장님께 또 교육해달라고 하고&nbsp;</p><p>사진을 찍어서 첨부해야겠어요 ㅎㅎㅎ)</p><p><br /></p><p>한의원적인 치료들과 아이들 성장, 성조숙증에 설명해주셨는데</p><p>애엄마라면 진짜 궁굼할거같은것들을 잘 이해할수있게 설명해주셨어요</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>우리 이수한의원 이제 아이들성장과 성조숙증도 전문적으로 하니</p><p>동내있는 어린이 환자도 많이 왔으면 좋겠네요 ^^</p><p><br /></p><p>______________________________________________________________</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>저번에 나원장님께서 교육해주시는 모습을 못찍어서</p><p>다음 교육하실때</p><p>안잊어버리고 꼭 찍었습니다</p><p><br /></p><p>ㅋㅋㅋ</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>원장님께서</p><p>아이들 성장과 성조숙증의 대해서 설명해주시고 계십니다</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/805c4ecad50c4447.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth:320px; rheight:320px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTVfMTAg/MDAxNTEzMzM5ODQyNzQ1.KP7LCmeF8pckbiHlctgmA38p8TDdPZNGwa8vHdKd5zsg.h3eT6cm0REL83ikh5kUEvmvqZ2rTrjNFSKUFHpm6xnwg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171215_190921391.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E417398')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/805c4ecad50c4447.jpg\"><br style=\"clear:both;\" /><br style=\"clear:both;\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/5972b66b461898a7.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth:320px; rheight:320px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTVfMTM4/MDAxNTEzMzM5ODQzMjM1.UtC4UdN6ek0bpGlg_T24wDFgiZo-Z-GOWyR9wKdYWUIg.q8eBp0m9YmFCbdZGVGs6UbaE8XMKs9wfavg5j7FOgIcg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171215_190921031.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E417398')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/5972b66b461898a7.jpg\"><br style=\"clear:both;\" /><br style=\"clear:both;\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/07af37ff1b28ac73.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth:320px; rheight:320px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTVfMTA0/MDAxNTEzMzM5ODQzNDQ5.Hrfac35MYf7HkGgmHeSsFXTCxHUEdca_XxRWdqKLn7wg.9k3eGw-N2OZqEUgsyr37u00iPhGQHXZam_HcOWwNdfUg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171215_190920531.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E417398')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/07af37ff1b28ac73.jpg\"></p><p><br /></p><p>근데 우리 원장님</p><p>자꾸 뒤로 하고계셔서 얼굴이 안보이시네요</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>그래서 얼굴 보이게</p><p>자리를 바꿔서 설명해달라고 말씀드렸더니</p><p><br /></p><p>살짝 어색하신지</p><p>귀엽게 웃고계시네요</p><p>ㅎㅎㅎ</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br style=\"clear:both;\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/0b8dccc59482bbdb.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth:320px; rheight:320px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTVfMTgx/MDAxNTEzMzM5ODQzNjE3.TiBnZ5GHO0eYoj9wxLITnvWRNlgRvkT7ZHEkGfOMkkAg.i559t04Y0sylIBq9yLB_Fof7GxgJOpNdZgTP2gcZTD0g.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171215_190919945.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E417398')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/0b8dccc59482bbdb.jpg\">&nbsp;</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>(진짜 사진 첨부했습니다~ ㅋ )</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt;\"><b><u>12월18일 월요일</u></b></span>부터 이수한의원이 새롭게 오픈할 예정이니&nbsp;<span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">다음주에 뵐께요~&nbsp;</span></p><p><br /></p></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
